\s Guh 284 YESU NI UMUKIZA WANJYE
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Yesu n’Umukiza wanjy’ Utangaje, kuko Andutira byose, Niwe wampagaritse ku Rutare, Mpaboner’umunezero.\bd*
\pc \bdit Niwe wampagaritse ku Rutare, Mu gihugu cy’umutarwe, kand’Ampisha mu Rukundo rwe rwinshi, Andindish’ ukuboko kwe, Andindish’ukuboko kwe.\bdit*
